Your understanding aligns with others.

Red Pine translated the phrases as:
"use inaction to rule the world" and
"I do nothing
and the people enrich themselves."

<QUOTE PREVIOUSPOST="
&gt; Frequently
&gt;it is misinterpreted to mean doing nothing which can be
